I mean, literally
partisanship is

00:40:12.000 --> 00:40:14.190
more dangerous to this
country than al-Qaeda,

00:40:14.190 --> 00:40:15.441
far more dangerous.

00:40:15.441 --> 00:40:17.190
And it makes it a
national security issue.

00:40:17.190 --> 00:40:20.460
And I wish Congress
would see it like that

00:40:20.460 --> 00:40:28.032
and form a committee
devoted to somehow ending

00:40:28.032 --> 00:40:29.490
the partisanship
that is destroying

00:40:29.490 --> 00:40:34.270
this country because it
will destroy this country,

00:40:34.270 --> 00:40:37.170
probably faster than we realize.

